00:21:05.940 --> 00:21:08.700
to generate the data that you
need to test your application.

00:21:08.700 --> 00:21:11.520
So, you can see I've got a
target of 170 rows here.

00:21:11.520 --> 00:21:13.950
And then out of that 170,
