00:21:15.330 --> 00:21:16.560
So, here's that 50.

00:21:16.560 --> 00:21:18.510
I'm going to check out
my different task types.

00:21:18.510 --> 00:21:20.630
And now, I'm going to
go ahead and run this.

00:21:20.630 --> 00:21:23.450
So, once I've done these
eval results, here we go.

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:24.710
So, we can actually check out.

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:26.000
So, where were we before?

00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.770
We were looking at our
single frontier model,

00:21:27.770 --> 00:21:29.600
where we were just running 4.1.

00:21:29.600 --> 00:21:31.760
And now, we've run that
