You only can have this --

00:24:06.360 --> 00:24:08.190
if there's more than
a seven-hour trip,

00:24:08.190 --> 00:24:10.200
you can go do business or not.

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:12.720
Right? All of these
different sets of policies

00:24:12.720 --> 00:24:14.970
that are specific
for the scenario.

00:24:14.970 --> 00:24:17.520
The tool call validity,
the escalation accuracy,

00:24:17.520 --> 00:24:20.850
when does it need to go to a
